snippet: Roger Federer cruised to a 6-3, 6-1 win over Grega Zemlja of Slovenia in the first round at the World Indoor Tournament in Rotterdam, the Netherlands.
lead_paragraph: Roger Federer cruised to a 6-3, 6-1 win over Grega Zemlja of Slovenia in the first round at the World Indoor Tournament in Rotterdam, the Netherlands.
